This module creates the libaudiostream.a libary file.

WHAT IT DOES?
=============
libaudiostream is common module, is used by all voice features.
it can be seen as recorder, it can record the PCM of different sample rate, different channel from mic.
it can read down link data from speaker and sync with uplink data from mic

HOW IT WAS BUILT?
==================
It needs the following library from AOSP:

libutils, libcutils 

and the following libs from MediaTek:

    libstagefright, libmedia

HOW TO USE IT?
==============

user can call the fuctions in this library to control record and read uplink data/downlink data.
